Name:			gpaw
Version:		20.1.0
Release:		2%{?dist}
Summary:		A grid-based real-space PAW method DFT code

License:		GPLv3+
URL:			https://wiki.fysik.dtu.dk/gpaw/
# Note that this is aadc02d3791ca874ec683ab46f1af369d2c10dd1 due to https://gitlab.com/gpaw/gpaw/-/issues/266
